# Warhammer Race stats file
#
# Various fields available:
#         Name -	Any string, name of race 
#         Move -	Movement in inches, unarmoured/armoured value separated by '/' 
#       WSkill -	Racial Weapon (melee) Skill
#       BSkill -	Racial Bow (missile) Skill
#         WStr -	Strength of Weapon (melee) Attack
#        Tough -	Toughness Factor
#       Wounds -	Number of Wounds
#         Init -	Initiative level
#      Attacks -	Number of Attacks
# Route_Factor - 	Route Factor
# 
#Name          | Group | Move | WSkill | BSkill | WStr | Tough | Wounds | Init | Attacks | Route_Factor
Name|Group|Move|WSkill|BSkill|WStr|Tough|Wounds|Init|Attacks|RouteFac
